Source: dmctool
Maintainer: Dean Serneevy <dean@serenevy.net>
Section: python
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10), dh-python, python-all, python-setuptools, python3-all, python3-setuptools
X-Python-Version: >= 2.6
X-Python3-Version: >= 3.2
Standards-Version: 3.9.1
Homepage: https://github.com/duelafn/dmctool

Package: dmctool
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}
Description: Tool to manipulate Jinja-template DMC files
 Galil controllers are a bit finicky about their input DMC. This script can
 process and reshape DMC files as well as remove comments and treat the DMC
 files as Jinja2 templates which makes writing DMC files much cleaner.

Package: python-dmctool
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python-jinja2, python-jinja2-apci
Description: Library to manipulate Jinja-template DMC files (Python 2)
 Galil controllers are a bit finicky about their input DMC. This script can
 process and reshape DMC files as well as remove comments and treat the DMC
 files as Jinja2 templates which makes writing DMC files much cleaner.

Package: python3-dmctool
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python3-jinja2, python3-jinja2-apci
Description: Library to manipulate Jinja-template DMC files (Python 3)
 Galil controllers are a bit finicky about their input DMC. This script can
 process and reshape DMC files as well as remove comments and treat the DMC
 files as Jinja2 templates which makes writing DMC files much cleaner.
